data.description: Motivated Sellers!! Come see this home that is situated on a sprawling 1.19-acre plot. This brick home offers timeless charm and comfortable living. Inside, you'll find 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths in a practical layout combining functionality and style. The kitchen features modern appliances and connects to a formal dining nook.  Step outside to a pool and covered patio for relaxing and entertaining your family and friends. Block away from the Coast to Coast connector bike path.  Check it out today!!
